---
title: Chive Tofu and Wild Rice with Buttery Green Beans
description: A classic 1-2-3 meal is sometimes all you need to please the whole family. Buttery green beans, savoury wild rice and chive-seasoned tofu are what you'll find in this elevated weeknight veggie dinner!
